parameters: \n<\n[5]>I saw that just now.\.\. You were thinking of walking away and pretending you did not hear me,\. weren't you?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Really now,\. I have gathered you are cold,\. a brute,\. smell a bit too musky for public decency,\. and perhaps one bad day from becoming a menace to society-\.-\.
\n<\n[5]>But I figured what with our experiences together we would at least be acquaintances!\.\. Truly,\. I have yet to receive a thank you for my efforts to aid you,\. huff!\.\.
Neneko groans,\. slumping her shoulders and gazing up into the sky.\.\. She sighs.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Fiiiiiine.\.\. Sorry.\.\. You've at least...\.\.\. made an attempt at being helpful.\.\. That's,\. uh,\. something,\. I guess.\.\.
Neneko stares at the vampire.\.\. Anzu stares back,\. expectantly.\.\.
Neneko groans even more,\. burying her face in her paws.\.\. She takes a deep breath and looks back to the still expectant noble.\.\.
Anzu looks rather pleased,\. her wings giving a single flap.\.\. She's smiling as if she'd eaten a full meal.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>There is still some hope yet~\. \BST[3]You are very most welcome,\. my dear~\.
\n<\n[1]>Have you gone batty for real down here?\.\. You're moodier than usual.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmph,\. as if you know how I usually am,\. my inattentive little stray cat.\.\.
She tosses her hair back,\. huffing.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You sure you're not just mad that it took so long to get here?\.\.
Neneko blinks,\. looking Anzu over.\.\. The vampire looks rather confused by her sudden attention.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Actually,\. where'd you even get that outfit?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>!!\.\. \BST[7]I have no idea what you mean.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Cuz I remember seeing this dress all torn up before,\. for some reason...\.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Why,\. Neneko,\. my cute,\. adorably intolerable kitten,\. I once more reiterate that I have no idea what you mean!\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Anywho!\.\. It is convenient that we've run into each other out here.\.\. \BST[1]Have you already been inside the Fortress?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmm.\.\. And what are your thoughts on it?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Fufufu...\.\.\. regardless,\. since you are here,\. I would like you to accompany me,\. kitten.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>I must have a meeting with the woman who calls herself the "Queen" of this Fortress.\.\. Important business and all,\. you see.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Gonna go meet Ruina,\. huh?\.\. What's that got to do with me?\.\.
Neneko gives a flat,\. disinterested look,\. her ears drooping.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Fufu.\.\. And I believe it would be valuable for you to be around for this conversation.\.\. \BST[5]Not everyday you get to see business be done.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Perhaps there will be information relevant to you,\. dear.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Haaaah...\.\.\. I hate that you're making sense.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmm...\.\.\. I wonder,\. \BST[4]do you perhaps have a problem with Lady Ruina?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Eh...\.\.\. not really,\. I guess?\.\. She didn't give me any problems.\.\. \BST[1]I couldn't really get much of a read on her.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>I see!\.\. Excellent.\.\. If she is at least willing to work with you then we may make more ground together then.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>She's kind of...\.\.\. bipolar.\.\. \BST[8]She got set off over nothing last time I met her and practically chased me out.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hah...\.\.\. I suppose I should not be surprised that both of you would have issue.\.\. \BST[4]Well,\. this may be a good chance to change her impression of you,\. then.\.\.
Anzu nods to herself,\. looking confident.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Right then!\.\. So,\. will you do me the favor of granting me your company,\. Kitten?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Actually,\. I've heard the Queen at this time has her...\.\.\. nightly activities...\.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Scandalous!\.\. \BST[1]Let's wait for the morning,\. shall we?
\n<\n[5]>Don't make me wait too much,\. kitten~
Anzu seems to be waiting for Neneko.\.\. It's clear she wants her to come closer,\. waving cheerfully and far too overly friendly for the cat's taste.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Oh,\. merely doing some plotting,\. you know how it is~\.
She rests her chin in her hands,\. grinning at Neneko.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Are you not impressed with my contributions to our little partnership,\. kitten?\.\.
The catgirl has a flat,\. unimpressed look on her face.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Indeed,\. my dear.\.\. Did I not give you a route to continue your little spelunking quest?\.\. An "in" to the dwarves,\. as it were?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>You are once more still not particularly good at showing your gratitude,\. but that can be something we work on.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmm?\.\. What was that?\.\. It certainly did not sound like a "Thank you Lady Anzu,\. your generosity and friendship is truly what I treasure most in this cruel abyss~\."
\n<\n[1]>Okay first of all even if I did thank you I'd never sound like that.\.\. What.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Second of all,\. seriously,\. we're doing the thanking thing again?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Yes.\.\. Go on,\. dear~\. I await it~\.
Neneko buries her face in her hands,\. groaning.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You know what?\.\. Fine.\.\. Okay.\.\. You've been the least useless person around here so far,\. so sure.\.\. Thanks,\. Anzu.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Come now,\. it is not so difficult.\.\. \BST[5]I wish to hear it,\. dear,\. in that adorably rough and scratchy voice of yours~\.\. "My sincerest gratitude,\. Lady Anzu~"
Anzu reacts as if slapped,\. before recovering quickly and clapping her hands together,\. a strained smile on her face.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Anzu is fine,\. actually!\.\. Only for you,\. however,\. dear.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Well if you've got your rocks off for the day from that,\. I'm out.\.\. Guardian to kill,\. lift to use,\. you know how it is.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Ah,\. just hold a moment,\. dear!\.\. Really now,\. in such a rush.\.\. I did in fact call you over for a reason,\. you know.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>As you know,\. I have my own little personal matters down below I must take care of.\.\. Problematic working conditions I would like to bring up with certain people,\. and all that...~\.
\n<\n[5]>And as you also know,\. while I have been improving thanks to the ambient Mana in this layer,\. I am,\. ahem,\. not quite up to my best shape at the moment.\.\.
Neneko grumbles.\.\. She has a feeling she knows where this is going.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>I would much prefer fixing that sooner rather than later.\.\. Preferably before we head on down,\. you see~\.
Anzu ignores Neneko,\. a rather winning smile on her face.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Anywho,\. since I have so graciously offered you my assistance,\. I believe it prudent I ask you to assist me in my own endeavors~\.
\n<\n[5]>After all,\. we can only help each other further like this,\. would you not say?~\.
Anzu looks happy as she claps her hands.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Now then,\. what do you say?\.\. Would you do a most important favor for your reliable,\. charming ally,\. partner in crime,\. beloved companion in this pit?~\.
\n<\n[1]>Nah.\.\. I'll pass.\.\. \BST[1]Got places to be,\. Calderas to Conquer,\. Guardians to beat up,\. you know how it is.\.\.
Neneko waves dismissively,\. turning to walk away.\.\. She'd wasted enough time with the bat's antics.\.\.
She'll skip out on dealing with her over dramatic reactions to being told no this time,\. thank you.\.\.
For some reason,\. though,\. Neneko shudders,\. as if a chill had come down on the Fortress.\.\.
The room was strangely silent,\. too.\.\. Neneko would have expected Anzu's shrill snooty gasping from being rebuffed again,\. but Anzu wasn't saying anything.\.\.
The catgirl was filled with unease,\. a sensation that something wasn't quite right.\.\.
She looks back at Anzu,\. to see if the bat had also noticed the weirdness going on.\.\.
But the blonde wasn't there.\.\. It's like she had vanished.\.\. Neneko was stunned.\.\. She didn't hear her get up,\. or anything!\.\.
The catgirl would deny that she was a little freaked out,\. nerves getting to her,\. but her fur had begun to frizz up in agitation regardless.\.\.
Was it getting darker?\.\. Where is everyone?\.\. Neneko tenses,\. peering around nervously.\.\.
She shivers.\.\. Things were looking bad.\.\. Her instincts were yelling at her,\. telling her that this room had become dangerous.\.\.
Yet her feet refused to move.\.\.
She felt like prey being stalked.\.\. A feeling she very much did not like being on this side of.\.\.
There was a chill down her neck,\. as if something was breathing on it.\.\.
Neneko flinches,\. making to turn around as she realized something had snuck up behind her,\. but-\.-\.
It's too late.\.\. Two sharp pricks pierce into her neck.\.\.
Fangs,\. biting into her.\.\. It stings,\. a heat going through her shoulder.\.\. She felt paralyzed,\. unable to even talk beyond an upset hiss escaping through her teeth.\.\.
She feels arms wrap around her,\. almost gently embracing her,\. breasts pressing against her back.\.\. A familiar shade of blonde hair hangs over her shoulder in her peripheral vision.\.\.
The crazy bat hums in response,\. almost purring as she sinks her teeth deeper into Neneko.\.\.
The cat is afraid she'd start sucking,\. draining her dry to power herself.\.\. She didn't know how Anzu moved so fast and so silently,\. but she was forced to admit that she was at her mercy.\.\.
But instead of sucking,\. Neneko felt a strange...\.\.\. pushing feeling in her shoulder,\. as if it were turning into jelly and something was making its way in.\.\.
Neneko shivers,\. mewling helplessly in discomfort.\.\. Anzu was...\.\.\. putting something inside her.\.\. An injection through the holes in her neck.\.\.
She didn't know what exactly,\. but it wasn't something good.\.\. Neneko's legs quaked,\. her stamina leaving her.\.\. She felt...\.\.\. frail,\. fragile.\.\. She didn't like it.\.\.
The pressure in her neck leaves as Anzu pulls her teeth out,\. and Neneko feels as if she would fall over if not for Anzu's arms around her stomach.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Haaah...\.\.\. your neck is so delicious,\. my dear kitten...\.\.\. it was hard to resist the urge,\. you see...\.\.\. the urge to take and take my fill of you...\.\.\.
The bat's hands run over Neneko's tummy and sides,\. caressing the cat fondly.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Why,\. I was simply giving you a gift,\. dear~\.
\n<\n[5]>That's what friends do,\. after all,\. is it not?\.\.
The bat's wings flap cutely as she giggles.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>They do things for each other~\. Give gifts,\. do favors...~\.
\n<\n[5]>And I consider you a very dear friend,\. Neneko~\.
Neneko grits her teeth as Anzu nuzzles her,\. rubbing her cheek against hers.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>I'd like to think we are two very good friends,\. who can always count on each other,\. you see...~\.
\n<\n[5]>And now that my powers are reawakening,\. I thought I'd just give you a little...\.\.\. taste of what I can do~\.
\n<\n[5]>To solidify our trust and relationship,\. you see...~\.  Before you ran off to the Caldera.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>I was a bit afraid you'd simply go ahead and ditch me at the first opportunity,\. so I am happy I caught you here first...~\.
\n<\n[1]>D-\.dammit...\.\.\. what did you put in me...\.\.\. I feel like I'm made of paper...\.\.\.
Anzu lets go of Neneko.\.\. The catgirl stumbles woozily,\. taking a few steps away from the vampire,\. covering the holes in her neck with a hand.\.\.
Anzu simply giggles innocently,\. watching Neneko's struggle.\.\.
Neneko grimaces,\. forcing herself to stand up straight.\.\. She exhales slowly to calm down.\.\.
With a strained breath,\. Neneko turns around to face Anzu.\.\.
Anzu beams brightly,\. clapping her hands together.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>It won't be too much of a detour,\. I'm sure.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>In the Amon Mines there's a passage untouched by the dwarves,\. \c[18]something of great importance\c[0] deep in its depths.\.\. It would be very...\.\.\. useful to me,\. simply put~\.
\n<\n[1]>You mean it's gonna help you get your dumb powers back?\.\.
Neneko grumbles,\. still holding her shoulder.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Perhaps so,\. kitten.\.\. Now then,\. it is simple.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Find me that Delicious Treasure,\. and I shall consider us even once more and ready to move on to the next step of my plans...\.\.\.
Neneko delivers an impressively flat stare at the flirty looking bat for a few seconds.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Right,\. I'm just gonna get to work and get this over with.\.\. Damn favors and friends...\.\.\.
She turns around and marches away,\. trying to keep her legs from shaking too much.\.\.
Ditching your friends definitely puts a load on your shoulders after all...\.\.\.
Neneko has received a \it[41]!\.\. Max \i[366] Health reduced by 2!\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Ah,\. my kitten~\. I wasn't expecting you back so soon~\. Did you bring my...\.\.\.
Anzu blinks,\. tilting her head and looking behind Neneko,\. spotting the trio of floating eye-\.like gem monsters following behind the feline.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>My my,\. I didn't think of you as the type to have pets.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>They ain't my pets.\.\. I went down to the Mines to get your...\.\.\. whatever it is you're looking for.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Ah~\. ...\.\.\.\BST[4]I take it there was a complication,\. then?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Yeah.\.\. I went as deep as I could and...\.\.\. ugh,\. I dunno.\.\.

\n<\n[1]>I think I might have found it?\.\. But there was just this...\.\.\. giant crystal wall blocking the way.\.\. There's no way I'm breaking somethin' like that on my own or carrying it back out.\.\.
The cat flicks her tail,\. a hand on her hip.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I kept lookin' around and then these 3 things started following me around and now they ain't leaving.\.\. \BST[7]What do you think?\.\. These look important and "delicious"?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Mm,\. I'm afraid I doubt my fangs could dig into these.\.\. Or that they would be very nutritional even if I could.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>But worry not~\. We have not reached quite a dead end yet!\.\. As a matter of fact,\. these 3 cuties will be lovely assistants in your little quest.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Mm...\.\.\. your little followers \C[18]wish to eat Mana\C[0].\.\. Once they've been charged enough I imagine they'd be able to "release" that charge to very explosive results.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>W-\.wait,\. these clingy little things are bombs?!\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Well,\. not exactly.\.\. But once you charge them,\. they will most likely eagerly blast down that crystal you were complaining about.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Urgh...\.\.\. I'm liking this detour less and less every second,\. batgirl.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmm...\.\.\. let me take a closer look...\.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>This one...\.\.\. seems to wish to gather \c[18]heat\c[0].\.\. Bring it somewhere very hot.\.\. I imagine somewhere in the inner workings of the Fortress may do.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>This one wishes for \c[18]electricity\c[0]...\.\.\. I believe your best bet would be in the Mountains to the north.\.\. The air in that region seems rather charged.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>And this one...\.\.\. hmm...\.\.\. \BST[1]I feel as if it wants something \c[18]similar to itself\c[0]?\.\. Perhaps a larger,\. older member of its kind.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hot,\. Zap,\. and Pointy Rocks.\.\. Great.\.\. Sounds like I'm going on a wonderful tour through this death pit today!\.\.

\n<\n[5]>I admit this was not quite within my expectations...\.\.\. \BST[5]but I believe you can do it,\. dear kitten~\. You're the most capable woman I have had the pleasure of speaking to recently~\.
Neneko's tail lifts and flicks about at the praise.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Perhaps you'd like some encouragement?\.\. A bit of motivation?\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Would you like a kiss for good luck...?~\. Or perhaps you'd like to wait for a proper reward from a most grateful lady once you return...?~\.
\n<\n[1]>Nyeh!\.\. Not in front of the kids,\. Anzu!\.\.
Neneko shields the eyes of the three monsters,\. backing away.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I'm just gonna go do...\.\.\. whatever.\.\. Seeya,\. nya.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>Huff...\.\.\. hard to get and shy as ever.\.\. I wasn't even going to bite that time...\.\.\. unless she asked~\.
\n<\n[5]>Hmm...\.\.\. let me take a closer look...\.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>This one...\.\.\. seems to wish to gather \c[18]heat\c[0].\.\. Bring it somewhere very hot.\.\. I imagine somewhere in the inner workings of the Fortress may do.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>This one wishes for \c[18]electricity\c[0]...\.\.\. I believe your best bet would be in the Mountains to the north.\.\. The air in that region seems rather charged.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>And this one...\.\.\. hmm...\.\.\. \BST[1]I feel as if it wants something \c[18]similar to itself\c[0]?\.\. Perhaps a larger,\. older member of its kind.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hot,\. Zap,\. and Pointy Rocks.\.\. Great.\.\. Sounds like I'm going on a wonderful tour through this death pit today!\.\.

\n<\n[5]>I admit this was not quite within my expectations...\.\.\. \BST[5]but I believe you can do it,\. dear kitten~\. You're the most capable woman I have had the pleasure of speaking to recently~\.
Anzu beams brightly,\. clapping her hands together.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>It won't be too much of a detour,\. I'm sure.\.\.
\n<\n[5]>In the Amon Mines there's a passage untouched by the dwarves,\. \c[18]something of great importance\c[0] deep in its depths.\.\. It would be very...\.\.\. useful to me,\. simply put~\.
\n<Dwarf Lookout>One wrong step,\. catgirl,\. and I'll crank it up!
\n<Dwarf Citizen>Many \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>proud dwarves\fn<GameFont>\fs[30] are fighting against those nasty kobolds around this Stratum!
\n<Dwarf Citizen>Go help them out if you can!\.\. Slay the lizards!!
\n<Dwarf Citizen>What you're looking at,\. beast?\.\. I know how to swing me axe,\. so keep your claws offa me!
\n<Dwarf Axeman>The Excavation Fortress is home ta all dwarves...\.\.\. what aboutcha?\.\. You're on our side o' history,\. aye?
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Aye aye,\. kittie.\.\. Ye came all the way up 'ere?\.\. What fer?
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Ya came 'ere to see the \c[18]Gem\c[0]?\.\. Pheh...\.\.\. good luck with that,\. Queen's wary o' strangers...
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Mov' along,\. kitten!\.\. Erryone got work to do 'ere!
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Th' Main Hall's ahead...\.\.\. Ruina's Throne 's past that...\.\.\. our Fortress' massive,\. don't get lost!
"Excavation Fortress,\. home to the proud dwarves,\. has served as a Company's Stronghold during the early days of the colonization."
"Long live the dwarves!\.\. Long live Ruina!\.\. To the conquest of the Hole!"

\n<Dwarven Blacksmith>Oi oi,\. you better have \G one you,\. kitten...
\n<Dwarven Blacksmith>Got \i[465] Splinters or \i[481] Shards on ya?
\n<Dwarven Blacksmith>If that's th' case...\.\.\. me forge is yours to use!

\n<Dwarven Forager>We ain't got much down here,\. and it ain't cheap,\. but not much reaches the Fortress.
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Mind yer manners,\. stranger.\.\. No enemy o' the dwarves escapes the Fortress.
